<br>
At level one the pet seems to land 7 or 8 nukes, and the damage is hardly noticeable over 40 seconds.  That is on solo exp mobs.. so on a raid it would likely drop to utterly useless.<br>
<br>
If all hits are for full, this pet will do about 1200 damage at level 1.  So about the equivalent of a fucused SofB every 9 min for no mana.  That is if the green pet can land on the mob, and if he retains LoS.<br>
<br>
The re-use time and short casting times are nice though.  If they fix the bolt animation it will *look* pretty impressive, and is kinda fun to have 2 pets up for a while for the low cost of 3 AA points. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=niien>niien</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(10/27/02 3:42:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=95.topic&index=42>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Servant of Ro casts...</span><hr size=1> this is a drake pet that just casts on target so you can have 2 pets at once with servant for 45 seconds<br>
